Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:04.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our neighboring country of Biscotti managed to regain peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:08.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The hero also seems to be enjoying a peaceful life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:13.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, our Princess Leo still looks troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:19.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So we, as her trusted aides, must find out what the whole story is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:10.52,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(800,0)\pos(470,359)}  「Declaration of War 」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:17.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, I advise against you starting \Nyour work early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:20.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've got a date with Sink this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:25.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I do something fun, I'd like to finish my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:29.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They have completed the weapon production.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:31.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, it was slightly earlier than planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:37.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The members of the Chamber of Commerce were very excited about two victories in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:38.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they worked it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:42.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They really deserve a treat then!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:46.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave that to Amelita's assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:47.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:51.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, I'm done with the morning's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:57.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Emilio, this is Princess's cerkle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:59.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's Haran.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:02.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one of the rarest kinds of cerkle in all of Flonyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:06.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're a rare one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:15.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink, sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.80,0:03:15.42,Dialogue Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:22.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haran seems to like you. I guess even cerkles like you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:24.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:27.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you could, please... just save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:35.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels so good to be moving this fast early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:36.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:50.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a pretty sight? This is my secret hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:59.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you normally do here, Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:05.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I take a relaxing stroll and eat my meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:07.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:11.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Before all that, how about some light exercise?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:11.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:15.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I sort of tried something out yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:25.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's how it goes. I'll toss this over to you, and I hope you catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:27.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:30.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:32.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:33.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:37.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:53.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:56.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:58.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:02.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do once I've caught it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:04.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:07.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it like this, then toss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:10.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you mean like this, and then I toss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:11.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:14.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:17.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:28.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:32.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:35.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's play more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:39.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna toss it real hard this round!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:44.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's high!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:48.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Sink! Try your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:53.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it really is a little too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:57.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Palladion. Form a staff! Make it fairly long!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:04.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Crest! Glide version!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:14.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. That's probably enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:30.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I last ran so much and yelled so loudly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:32.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, Sink, you're really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:37.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not only familiar with Ki-Power and \NCrest Attacks, you can also easily use Palladion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:41.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only can you transform it into weapons, \Nbut you can decompose it and make it into objects too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:45.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It just felt like Palladion was telling me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:48.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,what it could and couldn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:52.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that probably means Palladion really likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:56.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:57.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:07:03.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Palladion is a sword, right? \NSomehow I feel like it can't turn into a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:06.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll turn into one when the time is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:10.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps that means now it isn't the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:16.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the leader of Biscotti and \Nsupposedly the owner of the royal sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:21.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it has never awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:25.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Biscotti's royal sword... Was it the Holy Sword, Excellead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:29.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's actually half of the pair with your Palladion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:32.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's living proof of Biscotti's ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:37.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe a small ring like \Nthis has such a big story behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:42.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Even our neighbor, Galette, has two royal swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:46.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Whirlwind Demon, Granveil, and the Holy Sword, Ex Machina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:52.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are also similar pairs of royal \Nswords in other large countries as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:54.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:08:01.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll need to return Palladion to you when I return home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:03.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:11.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you were to summon me again, I'd need to borrow it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you still be able to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:18.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I go back, you can't summon me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:21.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:24.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then summon me! You must summon me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:29.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do so. I will definitely do so!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:31.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:35.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that'd be great too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:36.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thank you, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:41.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Should I not do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:46.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no. Um, I was just a little startled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:47.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:49.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:56.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, your hair's so fluffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is really smooth too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:04.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a little ticklish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this? {how about her boobs? then we can turn this into a hentai event}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:10.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not there! More over on this side...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:12.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:18.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how was the trip, Yukikaze?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:25.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a relaxing holiday with Lady d'Arquien and some others from the Onmitsu Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:29.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The letter just reported on the trip and the results of the hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:34.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We would have enjoyed more of your adventurous stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:39.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would really like to share that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:43.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One of her secret missions was to hunt for the wicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:48.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we cannot disclose anything without authorization.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:49.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:51.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:57.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But apart from that, I can tell you about every other thing we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:10:02.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's about the fun parts of our trip, I can talk about it anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:05.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let us hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:15.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Biscotti will welcome sunny and comfortable weather today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:15.80,Dialogue Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, how was your walk with Sir Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:20.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was very fun! He wants to do it again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:26.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Percy Gaudy from Wanlet Joumai. {i hate names. i have no idea what name is being said here.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:29.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just moments ago, the leader of the Galette Lion Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:32.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Excellency, Leonmitchelli, made a stunning declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:35.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, just take a look at the declaration footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:41.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With regards to Galette's athletic competition \Nthat is supposed to be held four days from now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:44.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby make a few amendments.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:50.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to two losses in a row, and also \Ntaking into account Biscotti's new hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:52.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as the return of the competent Lady d'Arquien,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:57.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be disastrous to our Lion Army's \Nreputation if we were to leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:03.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, I would like to initiate a new war with Biscotti.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:08.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Having considered conducting this war with such short notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:11.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll allow Biscotti to decide on any additional conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:15.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I also welcome members of the Chamber of Commerce and individual participation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:20.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, we have readied a large amount of cash prizes and awards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:25.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to make a fortune, people. Let's all participate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:31.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once Biscotti has agreed to this, tickets will be sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:35.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As we haven't got much time 'til the \Ncompetition begins, things will be rather hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:38.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll publish more thorough information later,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:43.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,as we'll need to properly explain to \Nthose who are interested in participating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:49.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, in order to better reward the winning country, I'm betting something extra on this.{she's betting the two swords for victory}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:58.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They are Galette's Holy Swords, the Whirlwind Demon, Granveil, and the Holy Sword, Ex Machina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:04.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're watching this, Princess Millhiore, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:10.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Biscotti will also place an equivalent bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:13.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that is of equal value to their country's Holy Sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:16.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she wants us to bet our Holy Swords too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:18.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is as if...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:21.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To the people of Galette and Biscotti,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:24.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,for the sake of your own country and also for yourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:29.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if you still have the courage to fight, join the battle immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:40.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the Holy Swords as a reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:42.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't the Holy Swords represent the country?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:45.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:51.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are times when the swords are temporarily lent out as a sign of friendship between countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:55.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps the people would think that's the case this time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:59.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, things actually appear to be a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:03.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into Princess Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:08.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is as if she really intends to invade Biscotti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:11.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that's not what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:17.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now she's already suggesting to use Biscotti's Holy Swords as reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:21.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amelita, the notice of declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:21.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:29.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The notice of declaration states that the period of sword keeping is no more than sixty days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:34.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the purpose of display and usage, it'll be based upon trust between the two countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:39.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be no illegal usage, and they will be returned within said period.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:43.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This means that they can use them \Nhowever they like during this period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:45.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any way we can decline this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:52.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But she has managed to capture the hearts of the people of both countries during the declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:58.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we refuse to bring out our Holy Swords, it'll look as if we're at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:03.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to fork out a lot if we want to compensate for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:06.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do? What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is problematic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:11.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there nothing I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:14.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it involves politics after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:18.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can only wait for Princess and the Leader of Knights to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:19.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:22.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:24.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap! You found me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:27.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you sent here as a forerunner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:29.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:32.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:35.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Emilio, what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:36.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Panettone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:40.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've discovered Galette's spy dressed as one of our knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:41.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:45.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only following orders
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:49.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to deliver a secret message to the hero, Sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:53.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A message for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:00.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:06.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:08.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:09.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:12.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about the upcoming war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:16.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Godwin and I are against this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:19.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot that we can't accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:20.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:24.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We were considering if Galette \Nreally intends to invade Biscotti.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:27.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister has overdone it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:35.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The history of Biscotti and Galette \Nsupporting each other dates back generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:38.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, out of the blue, she wants to invade.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's neither motive nor meaning to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.44,0:15:43.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After its announcement, with the \Npeople really looking forward to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:46.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this war is no longer avoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:52.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try my best 'til the last moment to find out why my sister suggested the Holy Swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:58.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if I don't succeed, if I'm\Nunable to understand her purpose,{line needs to be re-timed}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:01.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,please win this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:04.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaul, why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:07.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually kind of like Biscotti.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:12.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The food's great, I love the people and the scenery,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:13.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the princess is really sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:19.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, a Flonyard war should be a fun activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.28,0:16:22.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The participants, the supporters, the visitors,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:24.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the citizens that are not involved in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:28.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter if we end up winning or losing, it's important that we all remain happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.85,0:16:31.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the unhappy memories, we'll just leave it to the royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:37.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like reason will not be involved in the upcoming war.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:38.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:41.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:46.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't let the princess and the knights know that I said all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:48.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Gaul!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.31,0:16:51.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We'll leave this to you, Sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:55.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaul, one last question!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.06,0:16:59.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that our princess and \NPrincess Leo used to be best friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:02.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm not sure on that either,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:05.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess you could ask Amelita.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd know all about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:12.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like Prince Gaul made a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:14.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Let him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:19.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to expect anything of him and Godwin this round.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:23.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Godwin admires Prince Gaul, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:27.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good thing to be able to have a loyal subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:30.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be beneficial to his future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:34.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the ascendants of the two countries passed away,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:38.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Leo took really good care of our princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:43.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was as if they were blood sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:49.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the princess was young, she was always caring for and concerned about the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:53.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Together with Princess Leo, who was well versed in martial arts and crest attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:18:01.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they complemented each other and \Ntaught each other important things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:06.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since both of them became leaders, there weren't any crises either.{crises = plural of crisis}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:12.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though they saw less of each other, be it formally or informally, they've always remained on good terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:15.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably about half a year ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:24.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when, all of a sudden, Princess Leo became really worried about our princess and our knight army.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:29.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She suggested that Biscotti expand their armaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:37.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said we must prevent the princess from facing any potential danger and must protect her all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:39.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She kept desperately suggesting ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:44.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, since three months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:47.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's as if she'd turned into someone hard and cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:51.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She cut all ties with the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:57.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The princess was heartbroken from losing both her parents and her best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:19:01.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A sister-like friend had changed overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:05.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The relations between the countries turned bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:10.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, if Biscotti's Holy Swords also get taken away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:22.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will this be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:25.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:28.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the princess's order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:31.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We also need to be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:01.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:12.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure everyone saw the news this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:15.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,about Princess Leo's sudden notice of declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:19.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the matter being so sudden, all of us were caught unaware.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:24.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The elders were shocked, and they even fell from their chairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:29.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thankfully they weren't hurt, \Nso none of you need to be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:29.22,Dialogue Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady d'Arquien, Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:33.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero? Amelita?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:39.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I became the leader, it seems \Nthat we've lost several battles to Galette.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:41.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although wars were meant to be happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:46.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wished that both parties would be able to celebrate victory, but that can't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:50.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But this doesn't mean that Biscotti is a weak country.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:56.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our failed battles up to date are completely due to lack of preparation and my incompetence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:20:59.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:06.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:08.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:15.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to prevent losing in the future, we've made many preparations within this half year.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:19.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Frianno's Chamber of Commerce has helped us prepare sufficient weapons and armories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:24.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The young knights have been training hard, and they've become much stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:26.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:34.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Biscotti is willing to accept Galette's declaration!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:46.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course we will accept the bet regarding the Holy Swords, Excellead and Palladion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:50.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason is because we will not lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:57.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's win this war!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:22:00.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's win it and grasp a happier tomorrow!
